  ('medical-tech-moex-03220', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-113-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於cytogenetic技術，下列敘述何者最不適當？', '["血液檢體適用於一般染色體檢查，羊水檢體適用於胎兒染色體檢查", "血液細胞培養液含phytohemagglutinin（PHA），可刺激T細胞進行有絲分裂", "將細胞培養三天後，加入秋水仙素（colcemid），使分裂中之細胞停止於後期（anaphase）", "以Giemsa染劑進行染色，所得到之核型（karyotype），稱為G banding"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e3e83a07c05c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "40acdaaaecd6", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113020", "c": "308", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 71, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-03221', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-113-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '適合用於檢測白血病微量殘存疾病（minimal residual disease）的檢驗方法，其靈敏度至少要達到：', '["-1 10", "-3 10", "-5 10", "-7 10"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e3e83a07c05c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "40acdaaaecd6", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113020", "c": "308", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 72, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-03222', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-113-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '核苷酸變異發生在腫瘤基因的那個位置時，最有可能造成胺基酸改變而導致腫瘤蛋白質功能或活性的異常， 進一步促成腫瘤形成、轉移、抗藥等表現型？', '["外顯子（exon）", "內含子（intron）", "啟動子（promoter）", "強化子（enhancer）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e3e83a07c05c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "40acdaaaecd6", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113020", "c": "308", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 73, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-03223', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-113-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '就癌症而言，下列那一個基因的突變比例最高？', '["表皮生長因子受體（epidermal growth factor receptor, EGFR）基因", "TP53抑癌基因", "K-RAS致癌基因", "血管內皮生長因子（vascular endothelial growth factor, VEGF）基因"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e3e83a07c05c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "40acdaaaecd6", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113020", "c": "308", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 74, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-03224', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-113-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '已知肺腺癌病人如果表皮生長因子受體（epidermal growth factor receptor, EGFR）第858個胺基酸有突 變，對於特定酪胺酸激酶抑制劑將有不錯的治療效果。某位肺腺癌末期病人之不同採樣檢體的檢測結果如下 表，下列敘述何者最適當？', '["不建議此病人服用標靶藥物，因為僅有一種樣本檢測出突變", "推測此檢測結果應該是使用桑格定序法（Sanger sequencing）所完成", "此項檢測尚無查驗登記之體外診斷器材（IVD）可供選擇，皆須仰賴實驗室自行開發方法（LDTs）檢測", "病人可給與標靶藥物治療，使用一段時間後，可能產生次級突變（secondary mutation），造成用藥無效"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e3e83a07c05c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "40acdaaaecd6", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113020", "c": "308", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 75, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-03225', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-113-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於癌細胞失異合性（loss of heterozygosity）的敘述，下列何者最不適當？', '["常因染色體不穩定而造成", "常用西方墨點法來檢測", "失異合性的位置常有重要的抑癌基因", "常伴隨微衛星標記的比例改變"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e3e83a07c05c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "40acdaaaecd6", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113020", "c": "308", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 76, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-03226', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-113-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '為避免史蒂文生強森症候群，病患服用抗癲癇藥物carbamazepine之前，必須先檢查是否具有下列那種等位 基因？', '["CYP2C9*3", "CYP2D6*4", "HLA-B*1502", "HLA-B*5801"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e3e83a07c05c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "40acdaaaecd6", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113020", "c": "308", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 77, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
